quran[178]{c,v,t}:
  29,46,"Ur pnamaret At Tezmamt, siwa s wawal aéidan, siwa wid degsen idensen. Init: \"numen s wayen id irsen $uône$, id irsen $uôwen. Öebbi nne$, akked Öebbi nnwen, Yiwen. Nekwni $uôeS d imvuâen"
  29,47,"Akka ay ed Nessers, $uôek, Tazmamt. Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, umnen yis. Ger wigi, kra umnen yis. I inekôen issekniyen nne£, siwa ijehliyen"
  29,48,"Ur telliv temmalev kra n Tezmamt, uqbel tagi; ur p tepparuv, s uyeffus ik. Yili ad cukken inekkaôen"
  29,49,"Xaîi, neppa d issekniyen iberrzen, deg idmaren n wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni. Siwa imednas, i inekôen issekniyen nne£"
  29,50,"Nnan: \"a lemmer id rsen fellas, issekniyen s$uô Mass is\"! Ini: \"issekniyen ar Öebbi kan. Nek, d aneddaô kan, ipbegginen"
  29,51,"Ne$, ur steqnaâen ara s trusi $uôek, s$uône£, n Tezmamt, malen asen p. Deg waya, s tidep, aêunu, akked usmekti i ugdud iumnen"
  29,52,"Ini: \"Iqadd Öebbi, d anagi gari yidwen. Issen i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Wid iumnen di tkerkas, u ugin Öebbi, widak d imexsuôen"
  29,53,"Sêirin k $ef uâaqeb. Lemmer maççi d lajel ipwassnen, a ten id ias uâaqeb. Ih, a ten id ias, deqzalla, ur bnin"
  29,54,"Sêirin k $ef uâaqeb. Ih, Loahennama a ppezzi i ijehliyen"
  29,55,"Ass ideg ar asen isbur uâaqeb, sennig sen, akw seddaw ivaôen nnsen, ad Yini: \"jeôôbet ayen txeddmem"
  29,56,"A yimdanen iW iumnen, ni$ tamurt iW tewsaâ. Ihi, âabdet iyI, Nek"
  29,57,"Yal iman, ad ijeôôeb tameppant; sinna, $uône£ a d tu$alem"
  29,58,"Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad asen Nerr tanezdu$t di Loennet m t$uôfatin, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen, degs ad wekkôen. D asaâdi warraz n wid ixedmen lxiô"
  29,59,"wid iûebôen, ippeklen $ef Mass nnsen"
  29,60,"Acêal n lewêuc, ur d neppawi ôôeéq nnsen. Öebbi Iôeéq iten, u Iôeéq ikwen. Neppa, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  29,61,"Ma testeqûav ten: \"anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, i Inuben s yiîij akked waggur\"? A d inin, war ccekk: \"d Öebbi\". Ihi, acimi wexxôen"
  29,62,"Öebbi Issugut l$it i win i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, u Iwezzen as. Ih, Öebbi Issen yal cci"
  29,63,"Ma testeqûav ten: \"anwa id Isse$layen aman seg igenni, Issidir yissen akal, deffir tmeppant is\"? A d inin, war ccekk, \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ccekôan i Öebbi\". Maca, tegwti degsen, ur fhimen"
  29,64,"Tameddurt agi, di ddunit, siwa lhawiyya, d wurar. D axxam aneggaru, war ccekk, ay d amuddir, lemmer éôin"
  29,65,"Mara rekben di lbabuô, ad naâôen Öebbi, d idiniyen zeddigen $uôeS. Mi ten Isellek ar lberr, atnan la pcaraken"
  29,66,"Ad nekôen ayen i sen Nefka, ad zhun, deqqal ad éôen"
  29,67,"Day ur walan ara, Nerra loamaâ n laman, wanag la pwaxvafen imdanen i sen d izzin? Day ad amnen di tkerkas, u ad nekôen l$it n Öebbi"
  29,68,"Anwa i idensen kteô: win id isnulfan tikerkas af Öebbi, ne$ win irran tidep d tikerkas, mi t id tusa? Day maççi d Loahennama ay d tanezdu$t i ijehliyen"
  29,69,"Wid ijuhden ar loiha nne£, a ten Nenhu, war ccekk, s iberdan nne£. Ih, Öebbi Ippili ar lâuûam"
  30,1,Alm
  30,2,IôÔöumiyen rnan ten
  30,3,"deg wakal aqôib mavi. Deffir lexsaôa nnsen, ad rnun"
  30,4,"di kra iseggwasen. Lameô ar Öebbi, uqbel aya, u ssyen $eô da. Assen, ad feôêen lmumnin"
  30,5,"s rrbeê n Öebbi. Isserbaê win i S ihwan. Neppa, d Uzmir, Ipêunu"
  30,6,"D lemâahda n Öebbi. Öebbi ur Ipxallaf ara lemâahda S, maca, tegwti n medden ur ssinen"
  30,7,"Ssnen ayen id innunnten, di tmeddurt n ddunit. £ef laxeôt nitni stehzan"
  30,8,"Day ur meyyzen ara deg iman nnsen? Ur Ixliq Öebbi tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, siwa s tidep, akked lajel ipwassnen. Ih, aîas n medden i inekôen timlilit d Mass nnsen"
  30,9,"Day ur unagen ara di tmurt, ad walin amek tevôa d wid i ten id izwaren? Llan ifen ten tazmert, $zan tamurt, $elben ten akken i p âamôen. Usan ten id imazanen nnsen, s ubeggen. Ur ten Idnis Öebbi. Maca d nitni i idensen iman nnsen"
  30,10,D$a teqseê taggara n laâôuô. Skaddben issekniyen n Öebbi. Pmmaâliken fellasen
  30,11,"Öebbi Inezzu lxelq; sinna, Ippales it id. Sinna, $uôeS ara tu$alem"
  30,12,"Ass ideg ara d ijbu yimir, ad feqâen ibe$wviyen"
  30,13,Ur ten pselliken wid pcaraken. Ad nekôen wid pcaraken
  30,14,"Ass ideg ara d ijbu yimir, assen ad mfaôaqen"
  30,15,"Wanag wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ad zhun di tebêirt"
  30,16,"Ma d wid ijehlen, inekôen issekniyen nne£, akked temlilit n laxeôt, widak ar uâaqeb ara rsen"
  30,17,"Gedha s Öebbi, tameddit nnwen, taûebêit nnwen"
  30,18,"I Neppa ccekôan, di tmurt akked igenwan, tameddit u di pnaûfa n wass"
  30,19,"Issuffu$ ed amuddir si lmegget. Issuffu$ ed lmegget seg umuddir. Issidir akal, deffir tmeppant is. Akka ara d teff$em"
  30,20,"Seg issekniyen iS: Ixelq ikwen seg wakal. Aql akwen d imdanen tembwezzâam"
  30,21,"Seg issekniyen iS: Ixelq awen, segwen, tiâggaltin nnwen, a pzed$em yidsent. Irra garawen tayri, lmaênana. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud ipmeyyizen"
  30,22,"Seg issekniyen iS: lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan, amgirred ger tutlayin nnwen, akked initen nnwen. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i imusnawen"
  30,23,"Seg issekniyen iS: ives nnwen deg iv, deg wass, anadi nnwen n lfevl iS. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud isellen"
  30,24,"Seg issekniyen iS: Issenâat awen lebôaq, degs tugdi, asirem. Issadar ed aman seg igenni, Issidir yissen akal, deffir tmeppant is. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud ifehmen"
  30,25,"Seg issekniyen iS: s lameô iS, igenni akked tmurt bedden. Sinna, ma Isawel awen d, yiwen usiwel, seg wakal kunwi a d teff$em"
  30,26,"IneS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Akken ma llan, unzen aS"
  30,27,"D Neppa i Inezzun lxelq, sinna Ippales it id. D ayen i S isehlen mavi. IneS umedya aâlayan, di tmurt akked igenwan. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  30,28,"Ibbwi yawen d amedya, seg iman nnwen: day tcerkem d waklan nnwen, ayen i s ikwen N$at, d$a tâadlem yidsen? Day ten teppagwadem, akken teppemyagwadem garawen? Akka ay Nepfeûûil issekniyen i ugdud ipxemmimen"
  30,29,"Xaîi! Wid idensen teddun d lhawiyyat nnsen, ur ssinen. Anwa ara inhun wid Itlef Öebbi? Ur sâin imâiwnen"
  30,30,"Smil udem ik adini ar tidep, d lxelq n Öebbi akken id Ixleq imdanen. Ur illi ubeddel, di lxelq n Öebbi. Wagi d ddin amxallef, maca, tegwti n medden ur ssinen"
  30,31,"D imvuâen iS, êezzbet aS, beddet i téallit, ur ppilit seg wid ipcaraken"
  30,32,"seg wid ifeôqen ddin nnsen. U$alen d îayfat, yal akabar icôeê s wayen isâa"
  30,33,"Imdanen, ma iwwet iten wugur, ad naâôen Mass nnsen, d imvuâen iS. Sinna, ma Isêess asen aêunu, s$uôeS, a pwaliv arbaâ degsen pcaraken i Mass nnsen"
  30,34,iwakken ad nekôen i sen Nefka. Zhut! Deqqal a ppeéôem
  30,35,"Ne$ Nessader asen ed amvebbeô, i ipmeslayen $ef wayen i S pcaraken"
  30,36,"Mi Nesêess aêunu i imdanen, ad ceôêen yis. Ma têuza ten tucmip, seg wayen id urwen ifassen nnsen, ad aysen"
  30,37,"Day ur walan ara ar Öebbi Issugut ôôeéq i win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen i ugdud iumnen"
  30,38,"Efk as leêqq is i llezm ik, i ume$bun, i win id ibbwi ubrid. Ppif akka i wid ib$an udem n Öebbi. D widak ay d imerbaê"
  30,39,"Ayen teppakem n rrba, iwakken ad issem$weô ayla n medden, ar Öebbi ur issim$uô ara. Ayen tepzekkim $ef udem n Öebbi, d ayen ara ibuôekten"
  30,40,"Öebbi, ikwen id Ixelqen, sinna, ikwen I$aten, sinna, ara kwen In$en, sinna, ara kwen id Issidren. Day ara ixdem kra, seg waya, yiwen seg wid tepcarakem? Gedha s yiS, Aâlayan sennig wid pcaraken"
  30,41,"Ivehô ed lefsad di lberr u di yill seg wayen id urwen ifassen n medden, iwakken ad Isukk fellasen kra seg wayen xedmen, amar a d u$alen s abrid"
  30,42,"Ini: \"iniget di tmurt, muqlet amek tevôa d imezwura. Tegwti, segsen, pcaraken"
  30,43,"Err udem ik ar ddin amxallef, uqbel a d ias s$uô Öebbi, ass ur nepwexxiô. Assen, ad pwaferzen"
  30,44,"Win ijehlen, tijehli s mgal is; wid ixeddmen ayen ilhan, gemren i iman nnsen"
  30,45,"Iwakken ad Ikafi, s lfevl iS, wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan. Neppa, s tidep, ur Iêemmel ara ijehliyen"
  30,46,"Seg issekniyen iS: Ippazen ed avu abcir, ad awen Isêess, cwiî, seg uêunu S; ad iaâjel lbabuô, s lameô iS. A pnadim lfevl iS, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  30,47,"Ni$ Nuzen ed, uqbel ik, imazanen i igduden nnsen. Usan ten id, s ubeggen. Nerra d ppaô seg wid ibe$wven. Aslak n lmumnin d lwaoeb nne£"
  30,48,"Öebbi, id Ippaznen avu isselêayen asigna, a t ifser, deg igenni, akken i S ihwa, a t Issemfaôeq, a pwaliv ageffur a d iteffe$ segs. Mi t Issawev ar wid i S ihwan, deg imdanen iS, a ten tafev ceôêen"
  30,49,"Wanag, iu$ lêal, llan uysen, uqbel ad asen d i$li"
  30,50,"Wali lateô uêunu n Öebbi: amek id Issidir akal, deffir tmeppant is. Ih, d Win, s tidep, i Issidiren lmeggtin. Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  30,51,"Mara Nazen avu, ara walin ippiwôi$, a pdum, deffir es, tjehli nnsen"
  30,52,"Ma d keçç, s tidep, ur tezmirev a pperrev lmeggtin ad slen, ne$ iâeééugen ad slen i tnaâôit, ma u$alen $er deffir"
  30,53,"Ur tezmirev a penhuv ider$alen, mgal ttelfan nnsen. Ara terrev ad ak slen, siwa wid iumnen s issekniyen nne£. Nitni d imvuâen"
  30,54,"Öebbi, ikwen Ixelqen si ôehfan; sinna, deffir ôehfan, Irra tazmert; sinna, deffir tezmert, Irra ôehfan, akked ccib. Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Neppa d Amusnaw, d Aêernuk"
  30,55,"Ass ideg ara d ijbu yimir, ad gallen ibe$wviyen, ar siwa saâa segmi mmuten. Akka ay skiddiben"
  30,56,"Ad inin wid iwumi teppunefk tussna, akked liman: \"ni$ teqqimem di Tezmamt n Öebbi, ar ass n tnekra. Wagi d ass n tnekra, maca tellam ur tessinem"
  30,57,"Assen, wid idensen, ur ten tepsellik nndama ne$ asuter n ssmaê"
  30,58,"Ni$ Nefka, i medden, yal amedya di Leqwôan agi. Maca, mi sen d tebbwiv assekni, ad ak inin, war ccekk, wid ijehlen: \"kunwi d wid ireoonen"
  30,59,Akka i Iselle$ Öebbi ulawen n wid ur nessin
  30,60,"Eûbeô, ih, lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Ur k sêirin, wid ur nepputebbet"
  31,1,Alm
  31,2,Wigi d issekniyen n Tezmamt tuûwibt
  31,3,d nnhaya u d aêunu i iâaôviyen
  31,4,"wid ibedden i téallit, ipzekkin, ipputebbten af laxeôt"
  31,5,"Wigi, di nnhaya s$uô Mass nnsen. Wigi, d isaâdiyen"
  31,6,"Ger yimdanen, wid ippa$en awal n zzhu, iwakken ad nnetlafen seg ubrid n Öebbi, war tamusni. U fellas ttihin. I wigi, aâaqeb isdullun"
  31,7,"Ma mlan as issekniyen nne£, ad ibren s tem$weô, amzun ur asen isli, amzun âaégen as imeééu$en. Xebbeô it s uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  31,8,"Ih, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, leonanat isaâdiyen"
  31,9,"Degsen ad wekkôen. Lemâahda n Öebbi d tidep. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  31,10,"Ixleq igenwan, war tigejda ara twalim. Irra di tmurt idurar, iwakken ur tepzenzil ara yiswen. Iwezzaâ, degs, yal lxelq. Nessader ed aman seg igenni. Nessem$i d degs, yal tayuga tukyist"
  31,11,"Wagi d lxelq n Öebbi. Sseknet iyi d, acu d xelqen wid ur nelli d Neppa. Xaîi, imednas atnan di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  31,12,"Ni$ Nefka i Luqman ûûwab: \"snemmer Öebbi. Win isnemmiren, isnemmir kan i iman is. Ma d wid ijehlen, ihi, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz"
  31,13,"Mi inna Luqman i mmi s, la t isselmad: \"a mmi! Ur pcarak i Öebbi. Ccerk, s tidep, d ddens abarar"
  31,14,"Nweûûa amdan $ef imawlan is. Imma s temêen s tadist is. Tuîva s, sin iseggwasen. Snemmer iyI, u i imawlan ik. Tu$alin $uôI"
  31,15,"Ma êeppmen fellak, ad iyI tcarkev ayen ur tessinev, ur asen teddu di leb$i. Illi yidsen d uwqim di ddunit. Ddu d ubrid n wid isteôoâen $uôI. Sinna, tu$alin nnwen $uôI, ad awen Mle$ ayen txeddmem"
  31,16,"Ih, a mmi, xas am taéeyt uâaqqa ucceryad, ara yilin di teéôut, ne$ deg igenwan, ne$ di tmurt, a p id Iawi Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Laîif, Iéôa"
  31,17,"A mmi, bedd i téallit, ameô lewqama, îîixxeô i wayen n dir, eûbeô i wayen ara k id iasen! Aya, s tidep, seg uâzzem i lumuô"
  31,18,"Ur sxunzuô ar medden, ur teddu di tmurt s îî$aya! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iêemmel yal imnefxi, amzuxi"
  31,19,"Iôqiq di tikli k, ssers ûûut ik! Ni$ ûûut ucmit mavi, d win n ye$yal"
  31,20,"Day ur twalam ara, Inub Öebbi fellawen s wayen akw illan deg igenwan, akked wayen illan di tmurt? Isserwa yawen l$it iS, uvhiô, uffir. U llan l$aci i ipnamaren $ef Öebbi, war tamusni, ne$ nnhaya, ne$ Tazmamt timnewweôt"
  31,21,"Ma nnan asen: \"ddut akked wayen id Issader Öebbi\", a d inin: \"xaîi, a neddu akked wayen id nufa ar imezwura nne$\". I ma Cciîan atan la ten inecced ar uâaqeb n tmes"
  31,22,"Win ifkan i Öebbi udem amvuâ, u neppa d aâeôvi, iîîef deg ufus iûeêêan mavi. Ar Öebbi, tu$alin n lumuô"
  31,23,"Win ijehlen, ur k t$webben tjehli s! £uône£, tu$alin nnsen; ad asen Nini acu xedmen. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa i illan deg idmaren"
  31,24,"A ten Neoo ad zhun cwiî, sinna, a Nêeppem fellasen aâaqeb iwaâôen"
  31,25,"Ma testeqûav ten: \"anwa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan\"? A d inin, war ccekk: \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ccekôan i Öebbi\". Maca, tegwti degsen, ur ssinen"
  31,26,"I Öebbi i illan akw di tmurt akked igenwan. Ih, Öebbi d Asâay, d Amaâzuz"
  31,27,"Xas lukan ttjuô akw n ddunit d leqlamat, u yill, ernu yas ûa ilellen nniven, d lmidad nnsen, ur pqamen awalen n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  31,28,"Lxelq nnwen, tanekra nnwen, amzun d yiman yiwen kan. Ih, Öebbi Issel, Ipwali"
  31,29,"Day ur twalav ara, Öebbi Issekcam iv deg wass, Issekcam ass deg yiv. Iêeppem i yiîij akked waggur ad lêun, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ih, Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem"
  31,30,"Akka, acku Öebbi d Tidep. Ayen u$uô naâôen, war Neppa, d tikerkas. Öebbi, d Aâlayan, d Ameqwôan"
  31,31,"Day ur twalav ara ssfina, teppazal di yill s lqwedôa n Öebbi, iwakken ad awen d Issenâat seg issekniyen iS. Ih, deg wayagi, issekniyen i yal aûebôi isnemmiren"
  31,32,"Ma tesbur asen lmuja, am tillas, ad nujen ar Öebbi, $uôeS s ddin azedgan. Mi ten Isellek ar lberr, kra, degsen, îîfen deg wawal nnsen. I inekôen issekniyen nne£, siwa yal axeddaâ ajehli"
  31,33,"A yimdanen! Ëezzbet i Mass nnwen. Agwadet ass ideg ababat ur d ilehhu d mmi s, u mmi s ur d ilehhu d baba s, s wacemma. Ih, lemâahda n Öebbi, d tidep. Ur kwen tep$uôôu tmeddurt n ddunit. Ur kwen issefôa$ im$weôôi, $ef Öebbi"
  31,34,"Öebbi, s tidep, $uôeS tamusni n yimir. Issadar ed ageffur. Iéôa i illan di tâabbuvin. Ur iéôi yiwen acu ara ikseb azekka; ur iéôi yiwen anwa akal ideg ara immet. Öebbi, s tidep, Iéôa, d Amusnaw"
  32,1,Alm
  32,2,"Tarusi n Tezmamt, ur illi degs ccekk, s$uô Mass imavalen"
  32,3,"Ne$ a d inin: \"isnulfa p id\". Xaîi, neppat, d tidep s$uô Mass ik, iwakken a pnedôev agdud u$uô ur d iusi ara uneddaô, uqbel ik, amar ad pwanhun"
  32,4,"Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan; sinna, Iâannec $ef usgeld. Ur tesâim, war Neppa, bab, ne$ amcafaâ. Day ula d tesmektayem ara"
  32,5,"A d Iseyyi lameô seg igenni ar tmurt; sinna, ad iu$al $uôeS deg ibwass, lmudda s: agim iseggwasen, s leêsab nnwen"
  32,6,"Akka, Umusnaw n wayen iffren, u n wayen ur neffir, Uzmir Ipêunun"
  32,7,"I Iûûegmen akw ayen Ixleq. Inza d lxelq n umdan, si talaxt"
  32,8,"Sinna, Issuffe$ ed tarwa s si l$ella, degs cwiî n waman"
  32,9,"Sinna, Imesl it, Iûûuv degs, si ôôuê iS. Irra yawen timesliwt, iéôi, ul. Drus ay tesnemmirem"
  32,10,"Nnan: \"ma nweddeô di tmurt, day a d nepwaxleq tikelt nniven\"? Xaîi, nekôen timlilit akked Mass nnsen"
  32,11,"Ini: \"ad iddem ôôuê nnwen, lmelk n tmeppant i ippukelfen fellawen. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen a ppu$alem"
  32,12,"Lemmer a pwaliv ibe$wviyen, ad brun i iqweôôa nnsen, zdat Mass nnsen: \"a Mass nne$! Nwala, nesla; Err ane$ a nexdem ayen ilhan. S tidep, numen"
  32,13,"Lemmer i £ ihwi, yili Nefka, i yal ôôuê, nnhaya s. Maca, ad ivôu wayen Nni$: \"war ccekk, ad Acaôe$ Loahennama s leonun akked yimdanen, mejmulen"
  32,14,"Ihi, jeôôbet imi teppum a d temlilem d wass nnwen agi! Nekwni, ih, Neppu kwen. Jeôôbet aâaqeb, n lebda, ilmend n wayen txeddmem"
  32,15,"I iumnen kan, s issekniyen nne£, d wid, mara ten id mmektin, ara weddin ad knun, ara isbucuâen Mass nnsen s ccekôan, nitni ur pzuxxun"
  32,16,"Ppensaren d ibeôdiyen nnsen, seg imîeôêen, pnujun $eô Mass nnsen, s tugwdi d usirem. Seg wayen iten N$at, pseddiqen"
  32,17,Ur iéôi yiwen acu i sen Ffre$ n lfeôê. D arraz n wayen llan xeddmen
  32,18,"Win illan d lmumen, day am win illan d amed$ul? Ur aâdilen"
  32,19,"Ihi, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, leonanat imôaêbiyen, ara zed$en, ilmend n wayen xeddmeùn"
  32,20,"Wanag wid ide$wlen, di tmes ara zed$en. Yal tikelt ideg ara b$un a d ff$en segs, a ten rren $uôes, ad asen inin: \"jeôôbet aâaqeb n tmes i tnekkôem"
  32,21,"Ih, a Nessukk fellasen aâaqeb aqôib mavi, war aâaqeb abarar. Ahat a d u$alen s abrid"
  32,22,"Anwa i idensen sennig n win iwumi d dekôen issekniyen n Mass is, iu$al iwexxeô asen? Ih, a d Nerr ppaô seg ibe$wviyen"
  32,23,Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa. Ur ppili di ccekk af temlilit yideS! Nerra p d nnhaya i At Isôail
  32,24,"Nesbedd, segsen, iselmaden; nnehun s lameô nne£, mi ûebôen, u llan pputebbten $ef issekniyen nne£"
  32,25,"Ih, Mass ik, Neppa, ad Iêudd garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen i$ef mgarraden"
  32,26,"Day ur ten inha ara wayen Nesqucc isuta, uqbel nnsen? La leêêun $ef tnezdu$in nnsen. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen. Day ur sellen ara"
  32,27,"Day ur zôin ara Neppawi aman s akal aquôan; Nessuffu$ ed, yissen, iâaqqayen; teppen, segsen, nitni akked lmal nnsen. Day ur pwalin ara"
  32,28,"Qqaôen: \"melmi l$elb agi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  32,29,"Ini: \"ass n l$elb, liman n wid ijehlen, ur ten infaâ; ur pganin"
  32,30,"Ihi, wexxeô asen, ggani. Nitni, s tidep, la pganin"
  33,1,"A Nnbi! Ëezzeb i Öebbi, ur ppa$ awal i ijehliyen akked ixabiten. Öebbi, s tidep, Izga d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  33,2,"Ddu akked wayen i k d Ippuweêêan, s$uô Mass ik. Ih, Öebbi Ippuxebbeô $ef wayen txedmem"
  33,3,Ppkel $ef Öebbi. Iqadd Öebbi d Awkil
  33,4,"Ur Irra ara Öebbi sin wulawen di tfekka n urgaz. Ur Irra ara tilawin nnwen, i tmetlem ar iârar n tyimmatin nnwen, d tiyimmatin nnwen. Ur irra ara wid id tessekrem, d tarwa nnwen. Ayagi, d awal nnwen, seg imawen nnwen. Öebbi Issawal tidep. Neppa Ippawi d ubrid"
  33,5,"Ssiwlet asen am ibabaten nnsen; akka i iwqem ar Öebbi. Ma ur tessinen ara anwi ay d ibabaten nnsen, atmaten nnwen di ddin, d iqôiben nnwen. Ur illi u$ilif $ef wayen teffalîam degs, siwa ayen âammden wulawen nnwen. Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  33,6,"Nnbi iqôeb ar lmumnin, sennig iman nnsen. Tilawin is, d tiyimmatin nnsen. Wid ippemyilin, mqaôaben di Tezmamt n Öebbi, sennig lmumnin akked iminigen. Siwa ma tgam tajmilt i imeddukwal nnwen. Ayagi iura di Tezmamt"
  33,7,"Mi Neîîef si lambiyya lmitaq nnsen, u si keçç, si Nuê, Ibôahim, Musa, u si Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Neîîef segsen lmitaq lfayeq"
  33,8,"iwakken ad Iêtec imawlan n tidep, af tidep nnsen. Ihegga d, i ijehliyen, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  33,9,"A wid iumnen! Mmektit ed l$it ikwen I$at Öebbi. Mi d usan $uôwen iâsekôiwen, Nuzen asen d avu, akked iâsekôiwen ur twalam. Öebbi Izga Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  33,10,"Mi wen d kkan sennig wen, seddawat wen, mi zzint wallen, ulawen bbwven s ijuxax, tepmeyyizem yal ameyyez $ef Öebbi"
  33,11,"Dinna, ppwajeôôben lmumnin, enhezzen s leqseê"
  33,12,"Mi d nnan ixabiten, akked imehzulen n wul: \"ay $ d Iwaââed Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, siwa a$uôôu"
  33,13,"Mi d inna urbaâ segsen: \"a yAt Yatrib, ur illi umekkan i kunwi, u$alet\"! Kra segsen ssutren tsriê i Nnbi, nnan: \"ih, ixxamen nne$ aâran\". Nitni, ur llin aâran, b$an kan ad rewlen"
  33,14,"Ma kecmen ten id, si leriaf is, sinna, ssutren asen ad xubten, ad xubten. Cwiî kan ara kukrun fellas"
  33,15,"Ni$ llan âuhden s Öebbi, uqbel, ar ur ppu$alen ar deffir. Aâahed s Öebbi ad ippuqeîîi"
  33,16,"Ini: \"ur kwen tenfaâ trewla, ma trewlem si tmeppant, ne$ si îôad. Ara tezhum, siwa tallit wezzilen"
  33,17,"Ini: \"anwa wa, ara kwen ikksen seg ufus n Öebbi, ma Ib$a yawen cceôô, ne$ Ib$a yawen aêunu\"? Ur asen ppafen, war Öebbi, bab, ne$ asettaô"
  33,18,"Ni$ Öebbi Iéôa wid degwen, i ipâawwiqen, wid iqqaôen i watmaten nnsen: \"Yyat $uône$\"! Drus kan degsen, i ikecmen îôad"
  33,19,"D imceêêiyen ar loiha nnwen. Ma tusa d tugdi, a ten twaliv la k pmuqulen, tezzint wallen nnsen, am win tessexciwit tmeppant. Ma tekkes tugdi, a kwen gezren s yilsawen uqviâen. D imceêêiyen $ef lxiô. Wigi, ur uminen ara. Ihi, Imêa Öebbi igiten nnsen. Ayagi, d ayen isehlen i Öebbi"
  33,20,"£ilen ikabaren ur ôuêen ara. Lemmer a d asen ikabaren, ad ssirmen, ar nitni, di ûûeêôa ay llan, ar Waâôaben n ucluê, steqsayen fellawen. Lemmer llan yidwen, cwiî kan ara nna$en"
  33,21,"Ni$, i kunwi, Amazan n Öebbi d amedya amxallef i win ippaôoun Öebbi, akked was aneggaru, id ismektayen aîas Öebbi"
  33,22,"Mi walan lmumnin ikabaren, nnan: \"ayagi d ayen i $ d Iwaââed Öebbi, akked Umazan iS. Öebbi, akked Umazan iS, Ssawlen tidep\". Ay sen irna kan, siwa liman akked wannuz"
  33,23,"Ger lmumnin, llan irgazen i iîîfen deg wayen i$ef âuhden Öebbi. Garasen, wid iêellen timeôoiwt nnsen, garasen wid ipganin. Ur bedlen mavi"
  33,24,"Iwakken ad Ikafi Öebbi imawlan n tidep, $ef tidep nnsen, u ad Iâaqeb ixabiten, ma ihwa yaS, ne$ ad asen Issuref. Ih, Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  33,25,"Iééaâ Öebbi wid ijehlen, s iêecciô nnsen. Ur ppaddamen lxiô. Issuli Öebbi îôad i lmumnin. Öebbi Izga d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  33,26,"Issers ed, si lebôuj nnsen, wid i sen ifkan afus, seg wAt Tezmamt. Issekcem tugdi deg ulawen nnsen. Arbaâ ten$am ten, arbaâ têebsem ten"
  33,27,"Irra kwen tweôtem akal nnsen, ixxamen nnsen, ayla nnsen. D akal ur taâfisem. Ih, Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  33,28,"A Nnbi! Ini i tlawin ik: \"maday teb$amt tameddurt n ddunit, akked ccbuê is, yyamt a kwent $ite$, ad a kwent bru$, berru umâin"
  33,29,"Ma illa teb$amt Öebbi, Amazan iS, akked uxxam aneggaru, ihi, Ihegga d Öebbi, i tâaôviyin, segkwent, arraz ameqwôaêan"
  33,30,"A tilawin n Nnbi! Tid segkwent ara iawin abekkav ufviê, a ppeppuâaqeb berdayen. Ayagi d ayen isehlen i Öebbi"